{"id":319733,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/10/维权网-公民维权日，千余访民三办门前举行抗议/","date":"2013-10-25T17:48:13Z","modified":"2013-10-25T17:48:13Z","title":"维权网 | 公民维权日，千余访民三办门前举行抗议活动（组图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员唐韵报道）今天（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日）是每月最后一个周五的“公民维权日”，当日下午，全国千余名维权访民已经把三办（即国务院信访办、全国人大信访办和中纪委信访办）胡同挤得水泄不通。反腐维权的访民对政府还抱有一线希望拥向这里。但，失望也在这里。而在三办门口“恭候”维权人士的是几十辆警车、无数警察。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>到这里上访登记的维权者有几个能解决问题呢？几年、十几年、几十年在这里周而复始的填表登记，解决诉求则是寥寥无几。所以人们带着愤怒而来，留下悲哀而去。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>今天大家谈到最多的是要求释放陈永洲，保障记者合法权益。并对上海维权访民沈勇之死提出强烈抗议！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>日上午，家住浦东新区北艾路</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1765</span><span>弄</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">102</span><span>室的维权人士沈勇（男，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1959</span><span>年出生）被公安从家里带至六里派出所后仅一个多小时即突然死亡，沈勇的母亲也一度被公安带走不知去向。在场所有的维权人士抗议当局杀害无辜百姓！要求中央彻查此案！给全国人民合理答复，依法保障公民的生命权。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>大家针对近期沈勇、王德兰之死再次打出“严惩违法劫访，誓死捍卫人权！”的横幅。并继续打出“公民要求官员公开产”的横幅。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>参加公民维权活动的有：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>上海吴玉芬、韦亚珍、王永凤、郑培培、沈金宝，辽宁赵广军、林明杰、姜家文、王素娥、杨秀梅，吉林邓志波、杨忠和、张继新，黑龙江张宝珠、初东方、于丽华、王玉波、吕双丽，河北刘敏杰、段淑兰、孙秀琴，湖北徐彩虹，内蒙赵玉富，天津郑建慧，广西韦亚妮，宁夏宋玉芬等人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-q4TDbLGbrWk/UmphwXpcB0I/AAAAAAAAqGc/Aq2GAqz7Lek/s1600/mme.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-q4TDbLGbrWk/UmphwXpcB0I/AAAAAAAAqGc/Aq2GAqz7Lek/s320/mme.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-O7_o8wYgZnI/Umphz1DMl3I/AAAAAAAAqGs/0aidL64oQzE/s1600/mmexport1382700484487.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-O7_o8wYgZnI/Umphz1DMl3I/AAAAAAAAqGs/0aidL64oQzE/s1600/mmexport1382700484487.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-U_vZH4yev_I/UmphxrOxp3I/AAAAAAAAqGo/d5504khpuVE/s1600/mmexport1382700492176.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-U_vZH4yev_I/UmphxrOxp3I/AAAAAAAAqGo/d5504khpuVE/s320/mmexport1382700492176.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-u-tdq-H2fiM/Umph4z4rulI/AAAAAAAAqHA/t64b8d7aKPg/s1600/mmexport1382700516222.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-u-tdq-H2fiM/Umph4z4rulI/AAAAAAAAqHA/t64b8d7aKPg/s320/mmexport1382700516222.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-iDWJyeWRlk4/Umph1qjO3UI/AAAAAAAAqG0/X_BLf7OHKd4/s1600/mmexport1382700509438.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-iDWJyeWRlk4/Umph1qjO3UI/AAAAAAAAqG0/X_BLf7OHKd4/s320/mmexport1382700509438.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-X1D7Cl9RchI/Umph8H3K2aI/AAAAAAAAqHM/UfQG_k1C1EE/s1600/mmexport1382700523593.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-X1D7Cl9RchI/Umph8H3K2aI/AAAAAAAAqHM/UfQG_k1C1EE/s1600/mmexport1382700523593.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-zHgpv6nNYmo/Umph50wXJ2I/AAAAAAAAqHE/SSo_GWr2JKM/s1600/mmexport1382700594162.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-zHgpv6nNYmo/Umph50wXJ